video_title: You can change your personality ANYTIME #motivation #podcast #mindsetpodcast
transcript:
we're like brought into this world and
we're these perfect beings that are just
have no identity we don't know a name we
don't know what we're supposed to do and

like this is who I am and this is my

like the root word of personality in

have to get rid of the identity of who
you think that you are in in some

come from from their parents and then
that's reflected in being cheated on and
we start to build this I'm I'm unlovable

our relationships from then on out
unless we decide to change it
